channel.title: Looking for a great team! Many openings!
channel.description:
Hello, my name is Tom and i am currently trying to form a team of people that are willing to help maintain our runescape private server. We have quite a few positions open, they are: [s]Hoster: 1/1[/s] [s]Forum Designer: Taken (Me)[/s] Coders: 2/4 taken Designers: 2/4 taken Beta Testers: 0/6 taken
If you are interested in any of these positions... u may contact me by msn: Tom8004@gmail.com
It's all first come first serve!
If you want to join the team:
Name: Age: Position: Experience: Why you want the position you are applying for: MSN: (so i can contact you)
